name: swimmersymx
messages: Hey THEMOUSER, my team and I are big fans of the stream!
If you'd care to, check out our game, XPlorer Sky!
We think your audience would really enjoy if you streamed it!
Please? We can send you a free copy!
appeal_message: Listen, getting a streamer as big as yourself to stream our game would be life changing... please consider indie devs. Have a nice day
